title: Weekly Review With Clay and Buck H2 - Jun 4 2022
itunes:title: Weekly Review With Clay and Buck H2 - Jun 4 2022
description:
How could we all see inflation brewing, but Biden and Democrats didn't? Yellen admits she was wrong about inflation. Jamie Dimon says brace for an economic hurricane. Montage of Democrats and Biden saying inflation would be transitory. DOJ fights to reinstitute travel mask mandate. C&B parody: The Midterm Variant.
